    "This output module contains two prediction heads, each dedicated to one of the two output types (the next transaction attributes 𝑌 𝑛,𝑖 and the current transaction signals 𝑌 𝑠,𝑖, where 𝑖 ∈ {0,..., 𝑡 }).",
